      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some noticeable scuffs on the bumpers and a few minor door dings. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it may require some routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility and function over cosmetic perfection.",
