    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the pristine exterior finish to the flawlessly preserved interior, reflects a standard of maintenance that is truly unrivaled. Mechanically superior and aesthetically perfect, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than excellence. We invite you to experience a vehicle that defies its age and sets the benchmark for quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
